# Never copy host dependencies/build output into the Docker build context.
# (This is what caused `COPY ... cannot copy over an existing non-directory
# under apps/platform-api/node_modules/globals` — host pnpm symlinks collided
# with the image's installed node_modules.)
**/node_modules
.pnp
.pnp.*

# Build outputs — the image rebuilds these.
**/dist
**/.next
**/out
**/build
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# VCS / CI / editor metadata
.git
.github
.gitignore
.gitattributes
**/.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea

# Local env / secrets (keep the example so images can self-document).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Logs, coverage, scratch
**/*.log
**/coverage
graphify-out/
